metadata.description:
This is a first ever Virtual Reality AVATAR tokenized from within Somnium Space VR world. This is an NFT token which lives on Ethereum blockchain and proves authenticity of this creation. All files are securely encrypted and protected.     


Disclaimer: Please be aware that in case this Avatar is violating copyright laws or infringing third party IP it could be taken down and disabled anytime. Always do your own research before purchasing an Avatar. For more information please visit discord.gg/somniumspace
